const TickIcon = () => {
    return (
    <svg 
      className="tick"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
      width="25" 
      height="25" 
      viewBox="0 0 512 512">
      <title>ionicons-v5-e</title>
      <path d="M448,256c0-106-86-192-192-192S64,150,64,256s86,192,192,192S448,362,448,256Z" 
      /><polyline points="352 176 217.6 336 160 272" style="fill:none;stroke:#000;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:32px"/></svg>
    )
  }
  
  export default TickIcon
